      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/50e4a1f850c11d2b25d1d006760be5b8_2793932524622050024.png",
                "id": "talent51951",
                "key": "The Shape of Water\t",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The Shape of Water\t"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>This character gains <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro Application </span>and summons 1<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Bake-Kurage</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/b33ca2371d6c02d581a1a89570bc6fb8_431275816663321802.png",
                "id": "talent76430",
                "key": "Kurage's Oath",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kurage's Oath"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>. Heals all allied characters for 1 point. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ceremonial Garment</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Ceremonial Garmet</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>The character to which this is attached has their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Normal Attacks</span> deal +1 DMG.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character to which this is attached uses a Normal Attack:</span> Heal 1 HP for all your characters.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/47fcf95dc439392467286728a046b049_8699844660334643622.png",
                "id": "talent73695",
                "key": "Nereid's Ascension",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Nereid's Ascension"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>, heal your active character for 1 HP.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3036598406529091381.png",
                "id": "talent99066",
                "key": "Bake-Kurage",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/35428890/0e046eb8f7da357cc6b2ee42e058526a_8745730128578081493.png",
                "title": "Bake-Kurage"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_6115352327579685615.png",
                "id": "talent92664",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro Application</span></strong></p><p>When Hydro is applied without dealing any DMG, the Elemental Reaction triggered will ignore DMG-dealing effects:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: no effect</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: No effect</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: The target is unable to perform any Action this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: Creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro/Electro DMG</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/1ece3cf73687b4b134d3d9027b718b40_3143605269510858594.png",
                "id": "talent30880",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
